	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm not sure if Charisma does effect taunting. I'm a 52 HE pally with like 90 cha. I can taunt more then I want to sometimes with even high charisma. I think ones points value in this skill will determine it completely. Dunno how a mask to lower it will help much, but on the flipside; AC is decent for an untwinked 18-25th level player.&nbsp;&nbsp;My bard looted one and was hoping it would be for a quest but I havent found any such link.<br><br>Moralis, <br>52 Paladin of Life<br>Povar<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
