<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=100325773343659></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f100325773343659><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=1883&mid=100325773343659>CHA</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=1883&mid=100325773343659#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=86520><span id= >Slogha</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>27 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Oct 16th 2:42 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.66]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>For those of you thinking that a lower charisma makes you scarier, this isn't true!!<br><br>Charisma is not just how you look, it is your over all presence, your ability to influence others.&nbsp;&nbsp;This means that a higher charisma will relate to a higher ability to make someone afraid.  You can be very ugly and very charismatic, it would simpley mean that you have a lot of "presence."  This could be the way you walk, talk, carry yourself, anything.  I have tested this on my 35 necro several times.  I used this mask and several other items to lower my CHA as low as I could cheaply.  With my lowered CHA, I was completely unable to fear anything that wasn't rediculously low lvl.  Please don't post complete crap to these boards as you will lead people to do really stupid things, though they would probably deserve it for trying something dangerous without testing it themselves first, just because some idiot on a message board said it would work.<br>&nbsp;<br>Slogha Kovar<br></td></tr>
